issue.title: Request for integration with AWS Event Bridge for log shipping
issue.body:
We are interested in integrating tyk-pump with event bridge for our company requirements and also we are willing to take responsibility for developing the integration. To move forward, We would like to discuss with you about the ways to do it. Would it be a fine integration with sqs/sns features or the event bridge itself, or any other reasonable AWS services.
How do you plan to implement this integration if you have initial thoughts.

We are excited about potential of this integration and look forward to your guidance and collaboration.
Thank you
